LastExecution.description: The tick the command block last executed in

Command.description: The command stored in the command block

LastOutput.description: The last output of the command block

SuccessCount.description: The success count of the last command

auto.description: Whether the command block is automatically powered

conditionMet.description:
Whether the previous command block was successful when the command block was executed  
 This is always true for non-conditional command blocks

Name.description: Name of the owner, if missing appears as a steve head

Value.description: Base64 encoded JSON value of the texture

metadata.description: Custom data for the structure. Stores the data id for "DATA" mode

rotation.description: How the structure should be rotated

integrity.description: The chance for each block to stay

posX.description: The offset on the x axis for the structure position

posZ.description: The offset on the z axis for the structure position

showair.description: Whether to show invisible blocks inside the bounding box

sizeZ.description: The size on the z axis for the structure

mode.description: The mode of the structure block

powered.description: Whether the structure block has been powered by redstone

sizeY.description: The size on the y axis for the structure

sizeX.description: The size on the x axis for the structure

seed.description: The seed for the integrity randomness

mirror.description: How the structure should be mirrored

ignoreEntities.description: Whether the structure block should ignore entities

posY.description: The offset on the y axis for the structure position

showboundingbox.description: Whether the structure block should show the bounding box

CookTime.description: The number of ticks the item has been smelting for

Items.description:
The items in this furnace, with slots:  
 * 0: The item being smelted  
 * 1: The fuel  
 * 2: The output

Lock.description: The name of the item that a player has to be holding to open this furnace

CookTimeTotal.description: The number of ticks the item takes to be smelted

BurnTime.description: The number of ticks until the fuel runs out

Target.description: The UUID of the conduit's target

ExitPortal.description: The coordinates of where to teleport entities to

Age.description: The age of the portal in ticks

ExactTeleport.description: Whether the portal should teleport to the exact location

X.description: The x coordinate of the teleport location

Z.description: The z coordinate of the teleport location

Y.description: The y coordinate of the teleport location

progress.description: How far the moving piston has moved

facing.description: The direction the moving piston is moving

extending.description: Whether the moving piston is extending

source.description: Whether the moving piston is the piston head

blockState.description: The moving block represented by the moving piston

Book.description: The book that is on the lectern

Page.description: The current page the book is on

Ambient.description: Whether the effect particles are semi-transparent (like with a Beacon)

ShowParticles.description: Whether the effect particles should be shown

ShowIcon.description: Whether the effect icon should be shown

Count.description: The number of items in the stack

Slot.description: The inventory slot the item is in

Percentage.description:
For every modifier, multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the amount of the particular modifier.
 Functions the same as Operation 1 if there is only a single modifier with operation 1 or 2.
 However, for multiple modifiers it will multiply the modifiers rather than adding them

Additive.description: Adds all of the modifiers' amounts to the current value of the attribute

Multiplicative.description:
Multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the sum of the modifiers' amounts.

LeftOfUpsideDownDiagonal.description: Left of upside-down Diagonal (Per bend inverted)

RightOfDiagonal.description: Right of Diagonal (Per bend sinister inverted)
